data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home spanning 2,459 sq ft. The open-concept design connects living areas, including a well-appointed and a cozy dining space that leads to a private backyard with a patio This home has a spacious family room and living room features a gas fireplace. Upstairs, the master suite boasts a walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom, while 3 additional bedrooms share a full bath. A versatile bonus room offers customization options. With 2.5 bathrooms, this home ensures convenience. Enjoy modern amenities and classic charm in this 2,459 sq ft residence.
